entry: Today felt overwhelming. I woke up late and rushed through everything. At work, I couldn’t focus and kept worrying I’m falling behind. I snapped at a coworker, which I regret. After coming home, I felt drained but managed to cook myself dinner. Writing this down makes me realize I don’t give myself credit for the small wins, like actually eating well tonight. I just wish I could stop feeling like I’m always running out of time.
